1. Install NodeJS from below Site
  https://nodejs.org/en

2. Install angular CLI globally
  npm install -g @angular/cli@17
  
3. Create a new Angular application Standalone
  ng new <Application Name>

4. Create a new Angular application without Standalone
  ng new my-app --no-standalone --routing --ssr=false

5. Add Material Dependency to the Application
  ng add @angular/material
  npm install @angular/animations --save
  npm install ngx-toastr --save

6. Create Angular Component
  ng g c componentname

6. Create Environment Folder on to the Application
  ng g environments

7. Install Bootstrap
  npm install --save bootstrap
